updatePlayerStat(Player) - Method in class com.sucy.skill.api.player.PlayerData
Updates all the stats of a player based on their current attributes This method is very heavy, consume resources and notable by player Checkout other method such as PlayerData.updateWalkSpeed(Player) for a light refresh
This also does not update the player equipment You will need to call PlayerEquips.update(Player) before this function to update attribute/stats that comes with equipments
